<main class="wc-screen ">
  <div class="top-art" aria-hidden="true">
    <img class="hero-title" src="../../assets/football/home/hero-title-figma.webp" alt="">
  </div>
  <section class="modal-layer" aria-label="年龄限制提示">
    <div class="dialog dialog--center age-copy">
      <img class="age-emblem" src="../../assets/football/age-gate-dialog-header.svg" alt="">
      <h2>暂无法进入活动</h2>
      <p>仅限已完成实名认证的叫叫App注册用户（家长/法定监护人）参与。参与前请确认您已年满18周岁，系App使用者（学生）的监护人。</p>
      <div class="age-actions">
        <button class="yellow-btn">关闭页面</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
